data.description: Great Price! New Listing! Step into this exquisite Townhome in the prestigious Creel Walk community, nestled within the gated haven of South Fulton County. This chic two-story home offers a seamless blend of comfort and sophistication. Upon entering, you're welcomed by a generously sized family room that effortlessly connects to the kitchen, creating an inviting and open ambiance. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features a grand island that serves as the heart of the home, adorned with stainless steel appliances for both elegance and functionality. Venture to the upper level to discover the expansive master suite, a true sanctuary of relaxation. The suite boasts a trey ceiling, infusing an air of sophistication, and a spacious walk-in closet providing ample storage. The ensuite bathroom is complete with a separate tub and shower for indulgent relaxation.  This townhome also offers two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom on the upper level, providing versatile space for family or guests. Conveniently located, commuting is a breeze with quick access to major highways, and the proximity to the airport is a boon for frequent travelers.  Surrounded by a plethora of shopping and dining options, everything you need is at your fingertips. The Creel Walk community perfectly balances a serene, gated environment with the vibrant downtown Atlanta lifestyle just minutes away.  Seize the opportunity to call this stunning townhome yours. With its modern design, strategic location, and nice features, it epitomizes the ideal Atlanta living experience. Don't miss the chance to make this your home sweet home!
